---
import SiteLayout from "../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
return Astro.redirect("/partner/creator/", 301);
---

<SiteLayout
  title="YouTube & Social Media Creators | PoliceConduct.org"
  pagePath="/partner/auditor/"
>
  <main class="flex-grow-1">
    <section class="py-vh-3 bg-gray-100 border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb mb-3">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item">
              <a class="link-dark" href="/partner/">Partners</a>
            </li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Auditor</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-end">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-2">
              Value proposition
            </p>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">The Creator Intelligence Hub</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
              PoliceConduct.org does not replace your channel; we fortify your
              business.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">Built for</div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">
                  YouTubers and social media influencers
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted small">
                  Use structured data to find high-value audits and build cases
                  that hold up.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold">1. The heat map for auditing</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              Stop guessing where the next story is. Use community analytics to
              find precincts and officers with patterns that suggest likely
              First Amendment violations.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 d-flex flex-column gap-2">
              <li>
                Identify departments with high densities of refusal-to-identify
                reports.
              </li>
              <li>Spot spikes in interference-with-filming complaints.</li>
              <li>
                Prioritize travel and filming schedules using data-backed leads.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">
                  Business intelligence
                </div>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  We provide the data; you provide the footage. Find the next
                  audit with fewer miles and more impact.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-light border-top border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">
          2. Case file links for retention and SEO
        </h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Case file links
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Keep audiences engaged</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Give viewers a dedicated report link that houses evidence,
                  officer history, and relevant statutes after the video ends.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Subscriber updates
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Extend the story life</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Let audiences subscribe to report updates, keeping your
                  investigation active long after upload day.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">3. Turning clicks into case law</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Aggregated reports across a single department help support Monell
          claims by showing a custom or policy of misconduct.
        </p>
        <div class="alert alert-secondary rounded-0 border-dark">
          We connect incidents across precincts, officers, and time so attorneys
          can build a defensible record of municipal liability.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-gray-100 border-top border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">4. Why collaborate with us?</h2>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-bordered align-middle">
            <thead class="table-light">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">Feature</th>
                <th scope="col">Growth benefit for creators</th>
                <th scope="col">Legal benefit for attorneys</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Trend analytics</strong></td>
                <td>Find high-activity departments to optimize travel.</td>
                <td>Identify problem precincts for civil rights litigation.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Private detail hosting</strong></td>
                <td>Post evidence that might trigger platform filters.</td>
                <td
                  >Maintain timestamped records for pre-litigation discovery.</td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Update notifications</strong></td>
                <td>Build a subscribed audience around outcomes.</td>
                <td>Alert teams to new witnesses or related incidents.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Report linking</strong></td>
                <td>Drive traffic to a verified profile and case record.</td>
                <td
                  >Link complaints to demonstrate a custom or policy pattern.</td
                >
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div
          class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-lg-center justify-content-between gap-3"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-1">
              Ready to build the Creator Intelligence Hub?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
              We can share a partner resource kit with templates for linking
              your videos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="btn btn-dark rounded-0"
            href="/about/contact?whoami=Partner&message=I%27m%20interested%20in%20a%20creator%20partner%20resource%20kit%20and%20case%20file%20link%20templates."
          >
            Request the resource kit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
